        <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground mb-8">
          Available from all major Pune locations - IT parks, residential areas, commercial hubs, and landmarks.
          Professional drivers familiar with every area, society, and route. 24/7 service with transparent pricing.
        </p>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
